{"tid":2268824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2小鎮搶先開出總統票　川普暫領先拜登6票 16比10","createTime":"2020-11-03T05:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T08:54:51.000Z","uid":227801,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b87a1dffec905801adde2d5d7de30c95d490aabe","tid":2268824,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:46:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201103/CWXT64GADBA5DE6ITBI2FQ42YE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201103%2FCWXT64GADBA5DE6ITBI2FQ42YE%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EhZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=4ec07d62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201103%2FCWXT64GADBA5DE6ITBI2FQ42YE%2F&h=f6254455\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201103/CWXT64GADBA5DE6ITBI2FQ42YE/</a><br />\n美國今天（11/3）舉行總統大選投票，由於時差關係，選舉結果最快可能要到台灣時間明日（11/4）下午才會出爐。位於新罕布夏州的兩座小鎮今年不畏疫情，照常在當地時間午夜過後（台灣時間3日下午1時）便進行投票，其中一座選民僅5人的小鎮搶下頭香，成為第一個開出總統選票的投票站。雖然該座小鎮開票的5票全投給了拜登，但隨後川普便贏得另一座小鎮的多數選票，目前川普在兩小鎮的得票數為16，領先拜登的10票。<br />\n<br />\n13:20<br />\n另一座新罕布夏州北方小鎮米爾斯菲（Millsfield）緊跟著開出21張合格選票，川普獲得16票，拜登獲得5票。"},{"pid":"6b2c32aa8ce4829a51a357704c6587e2619e3b65","tid":2268824,"uid":201604,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"5人鎮(全鎮智障)"},{"pid":"b9f7a595cf446a8af5ba9f4e30681114859c80cb","tid":2268824,"uid":158585,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"Trump:我已勝選"},{"pid":"35e645a5c472b0f741582006bad21483ff3a907e","tid":2268824,"uid":35746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6b2c32aa8ce4829a51a357704c6587e2619e3b65","tid":2268824,"uid":201604,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"5人鎮(全鎮智障)"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"可能一家人 住一個鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e9